query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('com-interop',
'dependency-properties',
'dijkstra',
'docx',
'geocoding',
'load-testing',
'md5',
'mpmovieplayercontroller',
'richfaces',
'sencha-touch-2',
'singly-linked-list',
'tk',
'word-wrap');
